channel.title: Rush+Whitesnake+Greatful dead
channel.description:
Yea well these three bands are like pretty old now but I still love em...
Rush has one of the best drummers in my opinion I mean just check out the songs
-Closer to the Heart -Time stand still (One of there newer songs which was still a while back) -Limelight -Tom sawyer -Lakeside park -Fly by night
WhiteSnakes I just really like there style of how they play just check out these songs
-Now you're gone -Sweet cherry Pie -Here I go again on my own -Is this love (this is just like a slow song)
Well Greatful dead isn't the best band out there but I enjoy this one song.. -I will get by
